Description: RoboParty unified web backend server
 FastAPI + WebSocket server providing AT-command protocol for
 gamepad, Android app, head unit, MCP, and backpack clients.
 Streams IMU, battery, motor errors and manages policy execution.
 Runs on the RK3588 robot controller.
